    <h1>AI Content Writing</h1>
    <p class="description">The process of using large language models to draft, edit, or fully generate marketing content. A 2024 CMI survey found <strong>72% of B2B marketers already use AI in their content process</strong> — but the gap between raw output and publish-ready is enormous.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
